burn.t.sol
├── when burn caller is not bridge
│   └── it should revert with OnlyBridge
└── when burn caller is bridge
    ├── when transferability is off
    │   ├── when bridge caller is fromWhitelisted
    │   │   ├── it should burn tokens from the specified address
    │   │   ├── it should decrease the total supply
    │   │   ├── it should emit a {Transfer} event
    │   │   └── it should emit a {Burn} event
    │   ├── when address(0) is toWhitelisted
    │   │   ├── it should burn tokens from the specified address
    │   │   ├── it should decrease the total supply
    │   │   ├── it should emit a {Transfer} event
    │   │   └── it should emit a {Burn} event
    │   └── when bridgeCaller is not fromWhitelisted and address(0) is not toWhitelisted
    │       └── it should revert with TransferRestricted
    └── when transferability is on
        ├── it should burn tokens from the specified address
        ├── it should decrease the total supply
        ├── it should emit a {Transfer} event
        ├── it should emit a {Burn} event
        └── it should emit a {ERC20BridgeInitiated} event
